ECB’s Trichet Says There Is No Crisis of the Euro, Bild Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-15T10:10:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/ecb-s-trichet-says-there-is-no-crisis-of-the-euro-bild-reports.html
European Central Bank President Jean- Claude Trichet said “there is no crisis of the euro” and that
the ECB would deliver  price stability , in an editorial published
in  Bild am Sonntag  newspaper.  Trichet said the average inflation rate in the euro area
since the introduction of the single currency in 1999 was the
best result in the past 50 years.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  